Package org.hibernate.search.engine.search.query.spi

Interface SearchQueryBuilderFactory<C>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - The type of query element collector
    public interface SearchQueryBuilderFactory<C>
    A factory for search query builders.

    This is the main entry point for the engine to ask the backend to build search queries.
